      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, reliable choice for anyone needing dependable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the driver-side door, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and general wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been serviced regularly, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a functional car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
