    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me through every trip. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great pulling into the driveway, this is definitely the one! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next big adventure. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come on by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
