      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2002 BMW M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual, the drivetrain offers visceral engagement and precise gear selection. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced subframe, mitigating common E46 structural weak points. Equipped with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, the power delivery is predictable and linear. The double VANOS system has been recently serviced, ensuring optimal variable valve timing across the entire rev range. While showing honest signs of road use, the mechanical fundamentals\u2014including clutch take-up and compression\u2014are robust, making this a driver-focused specimen ready for the apex.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
