    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Executive Touring Sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated metallic charcoal that still holds a deep shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort. The light cream leather seats have been regularly conditioned and remain soft, showing only slight natural creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every feature\u2014from the heated steering wheel and dual-zone climate control to the premium navigation system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced exclusively at the dealership with a full record of synthetic oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with plenty of life left, and the brake pads were replaced just 3,000 miles ago. This is an honest, well-cared-for vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
